the 41-year-old virgin who knocked up sarah marshall and felt superbad about it is an american spoof of several of judd apatow 's films : the 40-year-old virgin , knocked up , superbad , and forgetting sarah marshall .   the main plot follows andy ( bryan callen ) , a 41-year old who desperately wants to lose his virginity , along with his teenage roommates who have similar goals .   according to producer and director craig moss , the original title was much longer , " more of a paragraph " , and had to be cut down to the final version .   on set , the film was called slumdog virgin , a reference to a spoof of slumdog millionaire included in the film .   the film was released direct to dvd on june 8 , 2010 .